name: DPC 2023 SA Summer Tour Division I – presented by ESB Liga Esports
description: Welcome to the DPC 2023 SA Summer Tour Division I presented by ESB Liga Esports Betsafe! We have the best 8 teams from the southamerican region, where they will be facing each other to reach the top 2 positions and win the spot to the Bali Major of the Tour 3, in addition to accumulating the highest amount of DPC Points and be closer to The International 12.
